                <h2 class="section-title">Research at SPIN</h2>
                <div class="research-intro">
                    <p class="lead">SPIN Academics is committed to advancing the field of pediatric neuroradiology through innovative research, collaborative studies, and evidence-based practice improvements.</p>
                    <p>Our research initiatives span from fundamental imaging studies to clinical outcomes research, quality improvement projects, and sustainable healthcare practices. We foster a collaborative environment where members can contribute to and benefit from cutting-edge research.</p>
